{"tid":22062,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【容忍有限度】雲尼亞里火都黎，揚言或棄用華迪、馬列斯！","createTime":"2016-12-04T08:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T13:16:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6425656ca7f18bab0e34b766ee76bb78181fe0","tid":22062,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"上季，占美華迪和馬列斯均是李斯特城勇奪英超冠軍的重要一員，但今季他們卻無法保持勇態，一同陷入低迷。對此，李城主帥雲尼亞里表示，自己或決定棄用二人，力保護級。<br />\n<br />\n雲尼亞里說：「是的，為何我不會換走占美華迪和馬列斯？我的責任是確保球隊以最佳陣容出戰。華迪與上季的不一樣，只是入球數字大減而已，在鬥心和合作性上，他依然處於高水平，但他知道若果繼續無法斬獲入球，他便會被擁有更佳入球效率的人取代。當然，我最希望華迪早日入球。」<br />\n<br />\n「馬列斯亦一樣。我經常擁抱他和親他，他需要更強的愛，但此子亦知道我的耐性會在甚麼時候耗盡。我想他們不會希望看到我動怒，然後將他倆置於後備席上的畫面，我的表情總是變得很快的！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sportbuzzer.emcdn.net/images/flex/crop/550x360/default/6c1db014f12d9a156e8d6a1d7fc21fa7_1479806816/jamie-vardy-hat-seit-dem-17-september-nur-einen-einzigen-pass-von-mitspieler-riyad-mahrez-erhalten.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportbuzzer.emcdn.net%2Fimages%2Fflex%2Fcrop%2F550x360%2Fdefault%2F6c1db014f12d9a156e8d6a1d7fc21fa7_1479806816%2Fjamie-vardy-hat-seit-dem-17-september-nur-einen-einzigen-pass-von-mitspieler-riyad-mahrez-erhalten.jpg&h=0652a12d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2265a016f8ccb51a571cf5833a562b373f068ab3","tid":22062,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"係愛啊，馬列斯"},{"pid":"7e6c16d1dce65b2214bee9afb367d5e58b86d4d5","tid":22062,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e6c72255b253cda84145c880716e5aff60b631","tid":22062,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"降班喇撚樣"},{"pid":"d7c682e4b4e773fa2d81851a61faca558101b3fa","tid":22062,"uid":31914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"馬列斯亦一樣。我經常擁抱他